h1_title: Best Settings on PS5 and PC
content: Not really a setting that makes a huge impact, but it will affect how vegetation looks in the distance. Going from high to cinematic doesn’t cause a loss of visuals, and your slight gain in framerate will result in your best possible outcome for this one.

Not really a setting that makes a huge impact, but it will affect how vegetation looks in the distance. Going from high to cinematic doesn’t cause a loss of visuals, and your slight gain in framerate will result in your best possible outcome for this one.
